Mean
Medium
Calculating mean and median

ðŸ“Œ à¦•à§‹à¦¡:

scores = [72, 88, 91, 65, 70, 85, 95, 79, 83, 77]
print("Student scores:", scores)

import statistics
mean = statistics.mean(scores)
print("Mean:", mean)

median = statistics.median(scores)
print("Median:", median)

Result =>
---------
Student scores: [72, 88, 91, 65, 70, 85, 95, 79, 83, 77]
Mean: 80.5
Median: 81.0

